OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1783952424
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'beloved' woman
OL,4,Cafter fatal house fire
OL,6,FThe family of a 'beloved' woman who
OL,7,Fdied following a house fire in
OL,8,FGloucester have paid tribute to her.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FAttlebridge Way in Kingsway just
OL,12,Fbefore 5:30pm on Wednesday 8th July.
OL,14,FOfficers attended the scene along with
OL,15,Fcrews from the fire and ambulance
OL,16,Fservices and a woman was taken to
OL,17,FSouthmead Hospital in Bristol with
OL,18,Fsevere burns.
OL,20,F42-year-old Amy Louise Stafford died
OL,21,Ffrom her injuries later that evening.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
