FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1783952424
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'beloved' woman
OL,4,Cafter fatal house fire
OL,6,FIn a statement, her family said: "Our
OL,7,Fbeloved daughter and sister Amy has
OL,8,Ftragically been taken from us. We do
OL,9,Fnot have adequate words to express how
OL,10,Fwe feel.
OL,12,F"A bright light in our lives has
OL,13,Fdimmed forever, our hearts will always
OL,14,Fseek out the warmth and love she
OL,15,Fbrought to us all.
OL,17,F"We would like to give our thanks and
OL,18,Fappreciation to all of the rescue
OL,19,Fservices who fought tirelessly to save
OL,20,Four darling girl." They added.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1783952424
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'beloved' woman
OL,4,Cafter fatal house fire
OL,6,F"Our love goes out to all Amy's family
OL,7,Fand friends near and far. Goodbye
OL,8,Fdearest Amy, sleep now, we are so
OL,9,Fproud of our independent lady."
OL,11,FA cordon was initially put into place
OL,12,Fat the address for emergency services
OL,13,Fto carry out an investigation.
OL,15,FScenes of Crimes officers, alongside
OL,16,FGloucestershire Fire and Rescue
OL,17,FService investigators, have now
OL,18,Fconcluded their search and assessment
OL,19,Fof the scene and are satisfied there
OL,20,Fis nothing to suggest third party
OL,21,Finvolvement.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
